            "id": 6318171,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 道瓊指數大漲1%，報48971.85點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間21日11:36，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>上漲483.26點（或1%），暫報48971.85點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-1.43%</li><li>近 1 月：+0.73%</li><li>近 3 月：+3.82%</li><li>近 6 月：+9.4%</li><li>今年以來：+0.22%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>成分股以聯合健康保險(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:UNH:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/UNH\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">UNH-US</a>)領漲。聯合健康保險(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:UNH:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/UNH\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">UNH-US</a>)上漲2.58%；耐吉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NKE:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NKE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NKE-US</a>)上漲2.28%；安進(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMGN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMGN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMGN-US</a>)上漲2.2%；漢威聯合國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:HON:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/HON\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">HON-US</a>)上漲1.87%；高盛集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GS-US</a>)上漲1.86%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對疲軟，嬌生(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:JNJ:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/JNJ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">JNJ-US</a>)下跌1.55%；可口可樂(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:KO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/KO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">KO-US</a>)下跌1.09%；微軟(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MSFT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MSFT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MSFT-US</a>)下跌0.97%；寶潔(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:PG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/PG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">PG-US</a>)下跌0.54%；威瑞森電信(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:VZ:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/VZ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">VZ-US</a>)下跌0.14%。</p></section></main>",
